    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>ex991.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>NEWS RELEASE DATED JUNE 24, 2025\n<TEXT>\n<HTML>\n<HEAD>\n     <TITLE></TITLE>\n</HEAD>\n<BODY STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif\">\n\n<P STYLE=\"text-align: right; margin: 0\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 8pt\"><B>Exhibit 99.1</B></FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<TABLE CELLPADDING=\"0\" CELLSPACING=\"0\" STYLE=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; font-size: 10pt\">\n<TR STYLE=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: left\"><TD STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; width: 50%\">News Release</TD><TD STYLE=\"text-align: right; width: 50%\"><IMG SRC=\"logo.jpg\" ALT=\"\">&nbsp;</TD></TR>\n</TABLE>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: bold 24pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: bold 14pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0\">Orla Mining Reports Voting Results of Annual\nShareholder Meeting</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 12pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0\">VANCOUVER, BC, June 24, 2025 /CNW/ - <B>Orla Mining\nLtd.</B> (TSX: OLA) (NYSE: ORLA) (&quot;Orla&quot; or the &quot;Company&quot;) is pleased to report the voting results for the election\nof its Board of Directors, which took place at the Company's Annual General and Special Meeting of Shareholders (&quot;AGM&quot;) held\ntoday. All nominees, as set forth in the Company's Management Information Circular dated May 9, 2025, were elected as directors of Orla\nat the AGM. Detailed results of the votes are set out below:</P>\n\n<TABLE CELLSPACING=\"0\" CELLPADDING=\"0\" STYLE=\"width: 100%; font: 15pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; border-collapse: collapse\">\n  <TR>\n    <TD STYLE=\"white-space: nowrap; padding: 0.5pt 2.05pt 0.5pt 3.95pt\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvet